Resource Profile: CH Audit Event for [ITI-65] Document Recipient

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/ChAuditEventIti65Recipient Version: 4.0.1-ballot-2
Active as of 2024-11-19 Computable Name: ChAuditEventIti65Recipient

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile is used to define the CH Audit Event for the [ITI-65] transaction and the actor 'Document Recipient'.
